=Description=

"Introduction of Haroon Sheikh at the World Interdisciplinary Network for Institutional Research (WINIR) conference as part of a roundtable "ICT, open societies and new institutions". 

Haroon gives an interesting talk about the global perspective on the organisation and control of the platform society.

Speakers on the roundtable: José van Dijck (Royal Netherlands Academy of Arts and Sciences), Haroon Sheikh (Dasym Investment Strategies) & Fredrik Söderqvist (Unionen)."

